      "span_text": "Note that since we need to calculate the attack losses during training, we must have access to the target classifier architecture as well as the weights (i.e. in the white-box settings), which is the basic limitation of Adaptive GAN. Yet, the recent work [CITATION_1] to address the black-box attack problem by training substitute networks can be combined with our approach.",
